author: Monica Chin
title: Snapdragon claims its new X Elite processor will beat Apple, Intel, and AMD
description: Snapdragon has announced its new X Elite processor, which is expected to ship in mid-2024. The company claims it will beat top chips from Intel, Apple, and AMD on select benchmarks.
